\par }{\expnd-2\expndtw-10\cf1 "Naturally."}{
\par }{\expnd-1\expndtw-8\cf1 "Not for these Two-legs. This was an unusual stage in their history and }{\expnd-1\expndtw-5\cf1 did not last. After the colonies on the various worlds grew and came to }{\expnd-1\expndtw-8\cf1 
