situation of which we are well aware. All of the Two-leg kingdoms, repub\-}{\expnd-1\expndtw-8\cf1 lics, aristocracies, etc., are simply tiny clots of worlds, each consisting of a dominant world and a few subsidiaries which, in turn, are forever seeking }
{\expnd-1\expndtw-6\cf1 their independence or being shifted from one dominant to another. This }{\expnd-1\expndtw-8\cf1 Earth is the strongest among them and yet less than a dozen worlds owe it }{\expnd-2\expndtw-13\cf1 allegiance."}{
